keyPolicies.policyDescription: Advocating for the extension of the Bakerloo line to Camberwell, including new tube stations at Herne Hill and East Dulwich.

keyPolicies.policyTitle: Getting a Fair Deal for Aylesbury Leaseholders
keyPolicies.policyDescription: Working for a fair compensation for leaseholders on the Aylesbury Estate, striving for them to be paid the market rate and for the local council to address and assist with relocation efforts.
